Package org.osate.ge.businessobjecthandling

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BusinessObjectHandler
    Handles the graphical behavior for a business object.
    CustomDeleter
    Interface which should be implemented by BusinessObjectHandler implementations to perform a custom delete operation.
    CustomRenamer
    Interface which should be implemented by BusinessObjectHandler implementations that do not support the built-in rename refactoring.
    RawDeleter
    Interface which should be implemented by BusinessObjectHandler implementations to perform a raw deletion operation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CanDeleteContext
    Contains contextual information for determining if a business object can be deleted.
    CanRenameContext
    Contains contextual information for determining if a business object can be renamed.
    CustomDeleteContext
    Contains contextual information for deleting a business object.
    GetGraphicalConfigurationContext
    Contains contextual information when requesting a graphical configuration from a business object handler.
    GetIconIdContext
    Contains contextual information when requesting an icon from a business object handler.
    GetNameContext
    Contains contextual information when requesting a name from a business object handler.
    GetNameForDiagramContext
    Contains contextual information when requesting the name used for the primary label for diagram elements representing the business object in the diagram editor.
    IsApplicableContext
    Contains contextual information for determining the applicability of a business object handler.
    RawDeleteContext
    Contains contextual information for performing a raw deletion of a business object.
    ReferenceContext
    Contains contextual information for getting the reference to a business object.
    RenameContext
    Contains contextual information for renaming a business object.
